		<title>3 things to know about cancer and your heart: Mayo Clinic expert shares tips to reduce risk</title>
		<link>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/3-things-to-know-about-cancer-and-your-heart-mayo-clinic-expert-shares-tips-to-reduce-risk/
		
